Detailed Description

The type is a constant name of the form CV_<bit depth>(S|U|F)C<number of channels>

The S/U/F abbreviations stand for S = short, U = unsigned int, F = float. For example CV_32FC1 is the type of a matrix with one channel of 32bit float values.

See also:
DepthType
